      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Subject: Apology and Update on Your Espresso Machine Delivery\n\nDear [Customer's Name],\n\nI hope this message finds you well. I wanted to reach out personally to address the delay in the shipment of your recently purchased espresso machine. We understand how much you were looking forward to enjoying your new coffee companion, and we sincerely apologize for the inconvenience this has caused you.\n\nIn the spirit of our commitment to customer satisfaction, we would like to offer you a 10% discount on your next purchase, as a token of our appreciation for your patience. We are also exploring ways to prevent such delays in the future, ensuring that our customers receive their orders on time.\n\nThank you for your understanding and continued support. We are eager to serve you again soon.\n\nWarm regards,\n\n[Your Name]\n[Your Position]\n[Your Company]",
